/2016/nsf16055/nsf16055.jsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NSF Office of Polar Programs Guidelines</a></span></p>', '<span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;A team member will upload data files and documentation to the NSF Arctic Data Center.\n\nThe data and associated files will be released through the NSF Arctic Data Center. Data and data products will be made available with as few restrictions as possible. These data and metadata will be made freely available for access and use by all via web-based distribution through the NSF Arctic Data Center.\n\nThe NSF Arctic Data Center will provide a recommended formal citation, including a persistent identifier or digital object identifier (DOI) for the submitted data which will allow the team members to cite and share the data.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:4867,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;4&quot;:[null,2,15724527],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;15&quot;:&quot;arial,sans,sans-serif&quot;}">A team member will upload data files and documentation to the NSF Arctic Data Center.<br /><br />The data and associated files will be released through the NSF Arctic Data Center. Data and data products will be made available with as few restrictions as possible. These data and metadata will be made freely available for access and use by all via web-based distribution through the NSF Arctic Data Center.<br /><br />The NSF Arctic Data Center will provide a recommended formal citation, including a persistent identifier or digital object identifier (DOI) for the submitted data which will allow the team members to cite and share the data.</span>', '{"meta": {"schemaVersion": "1.0"}, "type": "textArea", "attributes": {"cols": 20, "rows": 2, "asRichText": true}}', 0, 3, @default_funder2_id, CURDATE(), @default_funder2_id, CURDATE());
INSERT INTO versionedQuestions (id, versionedTemplateId, versionedSectionId, questionId, questionText, requirementText, guidanceText, sampleText, json, useSampleTextAsDefault, displayOrder, createdById, created, modifiedById, modified) VALUES (3320, 316, 2005, 965, '<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;When is the approximate release date of the data products?\nNote: Arctic Observing Network (AON) data must be deposited in a long-lived and publicly accessible archive within 6 months of collection, and Arctic Social Science Program (ASSP) research data must be deposited in a long-lived and publicly accessible archive within 5 years of the award date assuming no exceptions to the archiving requirements are requested.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:963,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;4&quot;:[null,2,15724527],&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}">When is the approximate release date of the data products?</span><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;When is the approximate release date of the data products?\nNote: Arctic Observing Network (AON) data must be deposited in a long-lived and publicly accessible archive within 6 months of collection, and Arctic Social Science Program (ASSP) research data must be deposited in a long-lived and publicly accessible archive within 5 years of the award date assuming no exceptions to the archiving requirements are requested.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:963,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;4&quot;:[null,2,15724527],&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}"><br /></span></pNSFsp><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;When is the approximate release date of the data products?\nNote: Arctic Observing Network (AON) data must be deposited in a long-lived and publicly accessible archive within 6 months of collection, and Arctic Social Science Program (ASSP) research data must be deposited in a long-lived and publicly accessible archive within 5 years of the award date assuming no exceptions to the archiving requirements are requested.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:963,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;4&quot;:[null,2,15724527],&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}"><strong>Note:</strong> Arctic Observing Network (AON) data must be deposited in a long-lived and publicly accessible archive within 6 months of collection, and Arctic Social Science Program (ASSP) research data must be deposited in a long-lived and publicly accessible archive within 5 years of the award date assuming no exceptions to the archiving requirements are requested.</span></p>', '', '<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;NSF Office of Polar Programs Guidelines&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:1049539,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;4&quot;:[null,2,15724527],&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;23&quot;:1}" data-sheets-formula="=HYPERLINK(&quot;https://www.nsf.gov/pubs/2016/nsf16055/nsf16055.jsp&quot;,&quot;NSF Office of Polar Programs Guidelines&quot;)"><a class="in-cell-link" href="https://www.nsf.gov/pubs/2016/nsf16055/nsf16055.jsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NSF Office of Polar Programs Guidelines</a></span></p>', '<span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Data products will be released no later than __________. (Examples are within 6 months of collection, within 5 years of the award date, etc.)&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:4483,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;4&quot;:[null,2,15724527],&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;15&quot;:&quot;arial,sans,sans-serif&quot;}">Data products will be released no later than __________. (Examples are within 6 months of collection, within 5 years of the award date, etc.)</span>', '{"meta": {"schemaVersion": "1.0"}, "type": "textArea", "attributes": {"cols": 20, "rows": 2, "asRichTe