e placed on the data? Consider the following.\n1. Who will be allowed to use the data?\n2. How will others be allowed to use the data?\n3. Will others be allowed to disseminate the data. \nNote: If you are planning on restricting access, use, or dissemination of the data, you must explain in this section how you will codify and communicate these restrictions.\nNote: if you plan to submit data to the Arctic Data Center (ADC) please refer to the guidance in the panel on the right.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:961,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}">How will others be allowed to use the data?</span></liNSFsli><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Will any permission restrictions need to be placed on the data? Consider the following.\n1. Who will be allowed to use the data?\n2. How will others be allowed to use the data?\n3. Will others be allowed to disseminate the data. \nNote: If you are planning on restricting access, use, or dissemination of the data, you must explain in this section how you will codify and communicate these restrictions.\nNote: if you plan to submit data to the Arctic Data Center (ADC) please refer to the guidance in the panel on the right.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:961,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}">Will others be allowed to disseminate the data. <br /></span></liNSFs/olNSFsp><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Will any permission restrictions need to be placed on the data? Consider the following.\n1. Who will be allowed to use the data?\n2. How will others be allowed to use the data?\n3. Will others be allowed to disseminate the data. \nNote: If you are planning on restricting access, use, or dissemination of the data, you must explain in this section how you will codify and communicate these restrictions.\nNote: if you plan to submit data to 