iew Board policies on the use of restricted data.</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">All data will be accessible to the public and subject to usage and dissemination restrictions under the CC-0 Public Domain Dedication License. </span></p>', '{"meta": {"schemaVersion": "1.0"}, "type": "textArea", "attributes": {"cols": 20, "rows": 2, "asRichText": true}}', 0, 2, @default_funder2_id, CURDATE(), @default_funder2_id, CURDATE());
